race.description: Golden Eagle & Derby Day 01/11 Mdn Plate
race.comment: MY CROWN (4) attacked the line strongly last start to grab second over this journey at Narromine. Hitting his straps now fourth-up. Expect to see him settle back early and charge hard late. NUCLEAIRE (14) showed good early toe at Moree over 950m before fading into sixth. Fitter now and if he controls the tempo he will be tough to reel in. THE BULLET (6) resumed at Narromine over 1100m and stuck on for fourth. Strips fitter and looks set to improve. Holds genuine claims. HUTT STREET (2) wasn't far away in fifth at Mudgee, staying in contention to the turn. Suited in this and cannot be overlooked. BIG BERTHA (8) lacks speed but has a turn of foot. Could storm late if the tempo is genuine.
